DESCRIPTION:This page's content changed since the last check. Visit the pa
 ge directly to review the update.\n\nWhat changed (text excerpt):\nAdded:\
 n  + FY27 Annual Attorney Registration is Open\n  + Attorney license renew
 al and Guardian ad Litem license renewal may be completed in the MyBoardAc
 cess portal from July 1 through August 31\, 2026 at 5:00 pm.\n  + Pursuant
  to M. Bar R. 4\,\n  + Registration documents and payments received after 
 August 31st will be assessed a non-waivable late fee.\n  + We greatly appr
 eciate your updated contact information\, proxy\, and IOLTA account listin
 g\, and service email for court service and notices.\n  + If your status h
 as changed since last year:\n  + new law clerk\n  + clerkship ended or is 
 ending soon\n  + retired seeking to be Inactive\n  + new judge\n  + no lon
 ger a judge\n  + active military or changing status\n  + seeking to become
  active again\n  + Before you register in the portal\, please contact\n  +
  execassistant@mebaroverseers.org\n  + to request a status change.\n  + Pl
 ease note\, if you still owe a CLE late fee your license renewal/registrat
 ion cannot be approved until that is resolved.\n  + Registration is comple
 ted online on the\n  + MyBoardAccess\n  + by clicking on the Renew Registr
 ation section of the Board's web portal. A confirmation email will automat
 ically be sent to you from informe.org when your registration is approved.
 \n  + 7/1/2026\n  + In re: Felix R. Hagenimana\n  + Single Justice\n  + Re
